    "name": "Baatamidar",
    "type": "creature",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Baatamidar",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "Baatamidars are drawn to destroy planar communities on the fringes where the Outer Planes touch the chaos of the <a aonid=\"19\" game-obj=\"Planes\">Maelstrom</a>. They resemble floating blobs of undulating, prismatic ooze with four quivering tentacles and dribbles of oily slime that always drip upwards.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Monitor</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"13\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Religion</a></u>)</b>: DC 47",
